headline: GoDaddy (GDDY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: GoDaddy trades at $183.97 per share and has moved almost in lockstep with the market over the last six months. The stock has lost 6.8% while the S&P 500 is down 2.4%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
